<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Health Articles</title>
  <style>
    .articles-container {
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      background-color: #f7f7f7;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    }
      a{
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
    h1 {
      color: #333;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .articles-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
      justify-items: center;
    }

    .article-card {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
      padding: 20px;
      max-width: 400px;
      text-align: left;
      transition: transform 0.2s;
    }

    .article-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
    }

    .article-image {
      width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }

    h2 {
      color: #007bff;
      margin: 10px 0;
    }

    .article-date {
      color: #666;
      font-size: 0.9em;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .article-content {
      font-size: 1em;
      color: #444;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="articles-container">
    <h1>Latest Health Articles</h1>
    <div class="articles-grid">

      <div class="article-card">
        <img src="https://tse4.mm.bing.net/th?id=OIP.sd-k47yR1TymvhfsF8WbkgHaDt&pid=Api&P=0&h=180" alt="The Importance of Regular Health Checkups" class="article-image">
        <h2>The Importance of Regular Health Checkups</h2>
        <p class="article-date">October 1, 2024 - By Dr. John Smith</p>
        <p class="article-content">Regular health checkups are crucial for early detection of potential health issues. Early intervention can significantly improve outcomes and lower treatment costs.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="article-card">
        <img src="https://tse4.mm.bing.net/th?id=OIP.qARnI9tfgfJrweF24NR4RwHaGk&pid=Api&P=0&h=180" alt="How to Maintain a Healthy Heart" class="article-image">
        <h2>How to Maintain a Healthy Heart</h2>
        <p class="article-date">September 25, 2024 - By Dr. Emily Clark</p>
        <p class="article-content">Maintaining a healthy heart involves regular exercise, a balanced diet, and managing stress. It is important to monitor your cholesterol levels and stay active.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="article-card">
        <img src="https://tse2.mm.bing.net/th?id=OIP.QtF2-9TXONJGUVFQsFXCXgHaEo&pid=Api&P=0&h=180" alt="Boost Your Immune System Naturally" class="article-image">
        <h2>Boost Your Immune System Naturally</h2>
        <p class="article-date">September 15, 2024 - By Dr. Alan Thompson</p>
        <p class="article-content">A strong immune system can be boosted by eating a nutritious diet, getting enough sleep, staying hydrated, and maintaining a positive mindset.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="article-card">
        <img src="https://tse3.mm.bing.net/th?id=OIP.1tO8WppB0EcA833YuRGG8wHaEK&pid=Api&P=0&h=180" alt="Tips for Better Mental Health" class="article-image">
        <h2>Tips for Better Mental Health</h2>
        <p class="article-date">August 30, 2024 - By Dr. Sarah Lee</p>
        <p class="article-content">Mental health is as important as physical health. Practice mindfulness, seek social support, and maintain a healthy work-life balance to boost your mental well-being.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="article-card">
        <img src="https://tse3.mm.bing.net/th?id=OIP.Mgc5torcODw4DDuV74yh7gHaEo&pid=Api&P=0&h=180" alt="Stay Hydrated for Optimal Health" class="article-image">
        <h2>Stay Hydrated for Optimal Health</h2>
        <p class="article-date">August 20, 2024 - By Dr. Robert Brown</p>
        <p class="article-content">Proper hydration is essential for every bodily function. Aim to drink at least 8 glasses of water daily and consume water-rich foods like fruits and vegetables.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="article-card">
        <img src="https://tse1.mm.bing.net/th?id=OIP.RJVUA0G_y-jLIECmiLa_BAHaEF&pid=Api&P=0&h=180" alt="The Role of Exercise in Disease Prevention" class="article-image">
        <h2>The Role of Exercise in Disease Prevention</h2>
        <p class="article-date">July 10, 2024 - By Dr. Kevin Adams</p>
        <p class="article-content">Regular exercise helps reduce the risk of chronic diseases like diabetes and hypertension. Incorporate 30 minutes of physical activity into your daily routine for better health.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
<%-include('footer.ejs')-%>
